<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>500 服务器错误 - 学生选课管理系统</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/bootstrap/css/bootstrap.min.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/bootstrap-icons/font/bootstrap-icons.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/style.css">
</head>
<body>
<div class="error-page d-flex align-items-center justify-content-center" style="min-height:100vh;background:var(--gray-50)">
    <div class="text-center fade-in">
        <div class="mb-4">
            <i class="bi bi-tools" style="font-size:5rem;color:var(--danger-light)"></i>
        </div>
        <h1 class="display-3 fw-bold" style="color:var(--danger-light)">500</h1>
        <h4 class="fw-bold mb-3">服务器内部错误</h4>
        <p class="text-muted mb-4">
            服务器遇到意外错误，请稍后再试。<br>
            <% if (typeof error !== 'undefined' && error) { %>
            <small class="text-danger">错误详情：<%= error %></small>
            <% } %>
        </p>
        <div class="d-flex gap-2 justify-content-center">
            <a href="/" class="btn btn-primary"><i class="bi bi-house"></i> 返回首页</a>
            <button class="btn btn-outline-secondary" onclick="location.reload()"><i class="bi bi-arrow-repeat"></i> 刷新页面</button>
        </div>
        <div class="mt-4">
            <small class="text-muted">学生选课管理系统 SCSMIS</small>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
</body>
</html>
